metadata.name: Queen of death
metadata.description:
The woman here is the embodiment of death, which dominates human life. The skulls surrounding her embody the fatal power of this gloomy life phenomenon, reminding us that an inevitable end will come for all of us. 
Every day should be lived in such a way as not to leave any regrets

—

1/1 hand drawn
2343 x 2890 px

By Vierlera 2023
